[Student "S"]
{SOUTH's 3\S supporting bid is enough to convince NORTH to make a slam try.

NORTH bids Blackwood 4NT. If SOUTH shows one Ace NORTH plans to bid 6\S, but 
when SOUTH bids 5\C NORTH settles for 5\S}

[Event ""]
